            {
                "name": "Guthallath Slumber",
                "type": "section",
                "sections": [],
                "text": "Entire civilizations have been swept off the face of Golarion due to the devastating rampage of a guthallath. But there is a light at the end of the tunnel, for after some time the guthallath ends its massacre in a swift yet seemingly random way. The colossus then finds a remote location deep in the wilderness, where it buries itself, entering a deep slumber for years\u2014if not centuries\u2014before awakening and beginning the destructive cycle once more.",
